						               													<description>Energy Conference is an environmental quiz game. In a semicircle you move your wooden figure from one field to the next. The distance is 18 fields. To move one field further, you have to answer a randomly selected question about the field topic correctly. These questions are summarized for each of four topics on a card and color-coded. In the case of difficult fields, you can call an energy conference with all players already present on the field in order to get to the bottom of the next three questions together or in competition with each other. If you are totally stuck, you can use a joker card, but it can only be used twice per player.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
